.0-1.0)\n    stale: bool                             # Whether memory is stale\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Text Relevance Scoring (BM25)**\n\n**File:** `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/bm25.py` (Lines 132-227)\n\n**Implementation:** Okapi BM25 ranking function\n\n**Key parameters:**\n- `k1 = 1.2` (default): Controls term frequency saturation\n- `b = 0.75` (default): Document length normalization (0=no length norm, 1=full norm)\n- IDF formula: `log((N - df + 0.5) / (df + 0.5) + 1.0)`\n- Stop-word filtering: ~50 common English words (Lines 17-78)\n- Suffix stripping: Basic stemming removing common morphological endings (Lines 99-108)\n\n**Preprocessing pipeline (Line 118):**\n1. Lowercase\n2. Tokenize (alphanumeric only)\n3. Remove stop words\n4. Apply stemming\n\n**Normalization (Lines 642-652):** \nRaw BM25 → `[0.0, 1.0]` via sigmoid: `score / (score + 5.0)`\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Decay Engine (Confidence Decay)**\n\n**File:** `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/decay.py` (Lines 181-228)\n\n**Time-based exponential decay:**\n\n```python\n# Default exponential decay\ndecay_factor = 0.5 ^ (days / half_life)\ndecayed_confidence = original_confidence * decay_factor\n\n# Clamped to [confidence_floor, source_ceiling]\n```\n\n**Tier-specific half-lives:**\n- `architectural`: 180 days (slow decay - project structure)\n- `pattern`: 60 days (medium decay)\n- `procedural`: 30 days (medium-fast decay - workflows)\n- `context`: 14 days (fast decay - session-specific)\n\n**Features:**\n- Uses `last_reinforced` if set, otherwise `updated_at` (Line 171)\n- Power-law decay option via `decay_model=\"power_law\"` (Lines 216-220)\n- Importance tags can boost effective half-life (Lines 204-212)\n- Profile-based overrides via `layer_half_lives`, `layer_confidence_floors` (EPIC-010)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Store Search Methods**\n\n**File:** `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/store.py` (Lines 566-602)\n\n**Primary search method:**\n```python\ndef search(self, query, tags=None,