* `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/reranker.py` (Lines 1-187)\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Takes top-20 candidates from BM25/hybrid scoring\n- Cross-encoder reranking improves precision\n- **Providers:**\n  - `NoopReranker`: Passthrough (position-based scoring)\n  - `CohereReranker`: Cohere Rerank API (optional dependency)\n- Fallback to original order on API failure\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Source Trust Multipliers (M2 Enhancement)**\n\n**File:** `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/retrieval.py` (Lines 65-72)\n\n**Default trust multipliers applied post-composite:**\n```python\n_DEFAULT_SOURCE_TRUST = {\n    \"human\": 1.0,      # Trust explicitly set by developer\n    \"system\": 0.9,     # Trust TappsMCP internals\n    \"agent\": 0.7,      # Agent-created memories less trusted\n    \"inferred\": 0.5,   # Inferred facts least trusted\n}\n```\n\nThis is a **post-composite multiplier**, not a weight component. Applied at Line 252:\n```python\ncomposite *= trust  # Reduces final score based on source\n```\n\n---\n\n### 11. **RRF Fusion (Hybrid Search)**\n\n**File:** `/mnt/c/cursor/tapps-brain/src/tapps_brain/fusion.py` (Lines 10-42)\n\n**Algorithm:**\n```python\ndef reciprocal_rank_fusion(bm25_ranked, vector_ranked, k=60):\n    fused = {}\n    for rank, key in enumerate(bm25_ranked, start=1):\n        fused[key] += 1.0 / (k + rank)\n    for rank, key in enumerate(vector_ranked, start=1):\n        fused[key] += 1.0 / (k + rank)\n    # Return sorted by fused score descending\n```\n\n**RRF constant k=60:** Reduces impact of rank differences (typical range 10-100)\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Files\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `models.py` | 82-211 | MemoryEntry with `source` field |\n| `retrieval.py` | 44-286 | Composite scoring, ranking, filtering |\n| `bm25.py` | 1-228 | BM25 text relevance implementation |\n| `decay.py` | 181-240 | Time-based confidence decay |\n| `store.py` | 566-602 | FTS5-backed search interface |\n| `persistence.py` | 547-571 | SQLite FTS5 search backend |\n| `reranker.py` | 1-187 | Cross-encoder reranking (optional) |\n| `fusion.py` | 10-42 | Reciprocal rank fusion for hybrid search |\n\n---\n\nThis architecture provides **deterministic, reproducible scoring** with configurable weights, time-based decay, source-based trust adjustment, and optional semantic/reranking enhancements."}],"totalDurationMs":63681,"totalTokens":73134,"totalToolUseCount":19,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1338,"cache_read_input_tokens":68644,"output_tokens":3152,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1338},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
