cored)} results, need at least 2.\",\n            \"query\": query,\n            \"store_metadata\": _store_metadata(store),\n        }\n\n    # Get actual entries\n    entries = [sm.entry for sm in scored]\n","numLines":50,"startLine":1190,"totalLines":2240}}}
