{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01K6UZDkd4omPNGwpzAyJ9B6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013VnDFGtCCKL59m6o97HXPi","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/mnt/c/cursor/TappMCP/.ralph/fix_plan.md","old_string":"- [x] M2: Add `source_trust` signal to composite retrieval scoring in tapps-brain. Defaults: human=1.0, system=0.9, agent=0.7, inferred=0.5. ✓ Added `source_trust` dict to `ScoringConfig` in `profile.py`, `_DEFAULT_SOURCE_TRUST` constants in both `profile.py` and `retrieval.py`, wired into `MemoryRetriever.__init__` (reads from `scoring_config`), applied as post-composite multiplier in `search()`. Updated `repo-brain.yaml` profile. 13 tests in `test_source_trust.py` covering config, wiring, ranking impact, custom overrides, unknown sources, and profile loading. **QA BLOCKED**: Git Bash shared library loading error — tests/commit deferred to next session.","new_string":"- [x] M2: Add `source_trust` signal to composite retrieval scoring in tapps-brain. Defaults: human=1.0, system=0.9, agent=0.7, inferred=0.5. ✓ tapps-brain: `ScoringConfig.source_trust` in `profile.py`, `_DEFAULT_SOURCE_TRUST` in `retrieval.py`, post-composite multiplier in `MemoryRetriever.search()`, `repo-brain.yaml` profile, 13 tests in `test_source_trust.py`. TappsMCP: wired profile `scoring_config` into `_ranked_search()`, `_find_entries_by_query()`, and CLI search. Added `source_trust_active` to search response, `source_trust` dict to `profile_info` response."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":858,"cache_read_input_tokens":62600,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":858},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4c2bbd2a-1a06-4e1e-9000-d7a8b9bf3b8b","uuid":"ce87c474